title: Level not showing up properly.
body: My boards' profile says I'm level 4, but I'm 6 and I'd like to post some stuff I made over at 'concepts and creations'.

replies.body: Thank you both! It's been fixed.

It looks like your boards profile has sync'd now!  Keep in mind that other regions of the boards may have their own level restrictions.  Please let me know if you have any questions, and welcome to the boards!
Post again and upvote / downvote my post.
